title: Simply Tai Chi with Graham Bryant Lorraine James DVDRip MP4
description:
This DVD bring to life the captivating movements of this ancient form of exercise.

Each movement is clearly explained and demonstrated and enables you to follow at your own pace.

Experienced instructors Lorraine James and Graham Bryant both demonstrate the warm-up exercises and then work through the routine step-by-step.

Tai Chi is an outstanding form of exercise because anyone can practice it anytime, anywhere, and in almost any state of health. Regular practice will help you increase your energy, concentration and flexibility, whilst reducing stress levels.
